msgid "When something happens (new comment, post, message, etc.), the plugin detects the event through Fluent Community, Better Messages, or Fluent Messaging hooks."
msgstr "當事件發生時（新留言、文章、訊息等），外掛透過 Fluent Community、Better Messages 或 Fluent Messaging 的 hooks 偵測事件。"

msgid "The server sends the notification to the push service (FCM for Android, APNs for iOS, etc.), which delivers it to the user's device."
msgstr "伺服器將通知傳送至推播服務（Android 為 FCM，iOS 為 APNs 等），再由推播服務傳送至使用者裝置。"

msgid "When the user clicks the notification, they are taken directly to the relevant page (post, comment, message, etc.)."
msgstr "使用者點選通知時，會直接跳轉至相關頁面（文章、留言、訊息等）。"
